#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31471"
msgid "Allows customization of default media flags without requiring outside hacks to the skin. This allows you to custom select which video container icons will be displayed for WebDL, 1080p, 720p etc. This can be reset at any time."
msgstr "E whakaae ana ki te whakarite i ngā haki pāpāho taunoa me te kore e hiahia ki te rāwekeweke i waho o te kiri. Ma tēnei e tuku i a koe ki te kōwhiri ko tēhea tohu ipu ataata ka whakaatuhia mō te WebDL, 1080p, 720p me ētahi atu. Ka taea tēnei te tautuhi anō i ngā wā katoa."

