#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31508"
msgid "This setting forces the media flag to resolution flag as 4K or 2160p providing user icon control without skin modifcations."
msgstr "Ma tēnei tautuhinga e hāpai te haki pāpāho ki te haki whakataunga pēnei i te 4K, 2160p rānei hei tuku i te kaiwhakamahi ki te whakahaere tohu me te kore e huri i te kiri."

