#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31511"
msgid "Dedicated addon for Madnox required for Piers+. Moves all free running scripts to a dedicated addon for security purposes."
msgstr "He tāpirihanga motuhake mō Madnox e hiahiatia ana mō Piers+. Ma tēnei e nuku ngā tuhituhinga herekore katoa ki tētahi tāpirihanga motuhake hei tiaki i te haumarutanga."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31512"
msgid "TMDbHelper provides several tools to assist skinners with retrieving information from TMDb, OMDb and Trakt APIs."
msgstr "Ka tautuhi a TMDbHelper i ētahi taputapu hei āwhina i ngā kaihoahoa kiri ki te tiki mōhiohio mai i ngā API a TMDb, OMDb me Trakt."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31513"
msgid "Wikipedia addon for Kodi."
