#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31514"
msgid "Advanced CinemaVision replacement that can be enabled to replace Madnox's built in simpler CinemaMode. Allows the ultimate CinemaMode experience and customisation."
msgstr "He whakakapi matatau mō CinemaVision ka taea te whakahohe hei whakakapi i te CinemaMode ngāwari o Madnox. E whakaae ana ki te wheako me te whakaritenga tino pai o te CinemaMode."

